txt_content:
比如,我新建一个mod叫testmod, 有个物品叫test.

主类我写了

(省略一堆import)

@Mod(modid = TestMod.MODID, version = TestMod.VERSION)
public class TestMod
{
    public static final String MODID = "testmod";
    public static final String VERSION = "1.0";

    static public Item test;

    @EventHandler
    public void preLoad(FMLPreInitializationEvent event) {
            test = new ItemTest();
            test.setUnlocalizedName("test");
            test.setTextureName("testmod:test");
            test.setCreativeTab(CreativeTabs.tabBlock);
            test.setMaxStackSize(64);
            
                GameRegistry.registerItem(test, "test");
                
    }

在ItemTest里我写了

package wzt.mod.testmod;

import cpw.mods.fml.relauncher.Side;
import cpw.mods.fml.relauncher.SideOnly;
import net.minecraft.client.renderer.texture.IIconRegister;
import net.minecraft.creativetab.CreativeTabs;
import net.minecraft.item.Item;
import net.minecraft.util.IIcon;

public class ItemTest extends Item {

        public ItemTest () {
                
        }
}

崩溃报告有一行是
Caused by: java.lang.NoSuchMethodError: net.minecraft.item.Item.setUnlocalizedName(Ljava/lang/String;)Lnet/minecraft/item/Item;
        at wzt.mod.testmod.TestMod.preLoad(TestMod.java:29)

TestMod.java的第29行是
test.setUnlocalizedName("test");

就算我先不setUnlocalizedName, 我先setTextureName, 先setCreativeTab,  都会出现java.lang.NoSuchMethodError

求解决






